text: Alida Impia Maria "Alie" van Leeuwen (13 August 1908 - 23 October 1991) was a Dutch diver. She competed in two events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1908 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Dutch female divers Category:Olympic divers of the Netherlands Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
